<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cancellation Policy - PingME</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      width: 90%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #222;
      color: #ccc;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #ccc;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Media Queries for responsiveness */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        width: 95%;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }

      footer {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Cancellation Policy</h1>
    <p>Thank you for shopping at PingME.</p>

    <h2>Order Cancellation</h2>
    <p>You may cancel your order within 2 days from the time of purchase. After this period, your order may have already been processed and cannot be cancelled.</p>

    <h2>Refunds for Cancellations</h2>
    <p>If you cancel your order within the allowed cancellation period, we will issue a full refund to your original method of payment.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about our cancellation policy, contact us through our contact page.</p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 PingME. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
